usally I talk to her through my shayari, so much so that 
nothing is left for me to talk to her in person


tasavvur
hakeekat

Alfaaz tatooltha baatein karne unse
jisse tasavvur me shayari karata hunn

Bhook lagi hai mujhe to zaroor muh chalaunga
Aam tu na mila to kya mai angoor khaunga


Mazak me kahi baat kuch aisa kar gayi
hasi ki baat ghlatfaimi me badal gayi


baton hi baton me lagne laga ke tum badl gayi


Kyun yakeen dilaoo main tumhe baar baar
